<paragraph blockId="3.[109,748,284,371]" pageId="3" pageNumber="20">Abdomen shining black. Tergites dorsally with short pale brownish bristles; basal tergite with long brown bristles at sides. Apical two segments and cerci brown dusted.</paragraph>
